---
title: Quick Asian Salt & Pepper Chicken Bowl with Honey-Soy Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: Salt and pepper are always there, ready whenever you need that extra push of seasoning, doing their duty in every dish. Now it’s their time to shine in this chicken and rice bowl. Salt and pepper beef is the standout, but don’t forget those honey soy veggies because we sure won’t!
